description:
So thin, they're invisible. Well, not quite. But they are our thinnest, most comfortable pads ever so you get the Invisible feeling with superior protection. Combine that with our unique BodyFit® shape that's designed to fit the contours of your body and move with you, and you get the ultimate comfort & protection. Our goal is that you won't even notice how good they are.

4 Layer InstaDry® technology for quick fluid absorption

Extra thin for comfort & security

Abosrbent core (Absorbs up to 10x it's weight)

Unique wing design stays in place
